{"tid":2357344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聲稱遭男教師拳打　辯方質疑口供不符　男警：我學歷低　口供寫得差","createTime":"2021-01-07T11:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T12:24:35.000Z","uid":50386,"like":15,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef0de7351561637127fedaefc929bff15b2cff9","tid":2357344,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:02:43.000Z","msg":"前年 9 月 8 日，有人於中環遮打花園舉行《香港人權與民主法案》祈禱會，演變為警民衝突，多人被捕。一名 27 歲教師被指於銅鑼灣襲警被控，他不認罪，今於東區裁判法院受審。聲稱被襲警員趙金今日供稱，他看見一名警長想搭被告膊頭，但不肯定是否有「掂到」，被告轉身逃走，他則追截並制服被告，期間遭對方揮拳打了面部一下。辯方盤問指，趙於其書面口供中指警長「搭住被捕人膊頭」，與其庭上口供有出入，<span class=\"red\">趙解釋指是他表達得不好，「口供係成日寫，但詞彙運用嗰啲，因為我學歷低，所以寫得差。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/聲稱遭男教師拳打-辯方質疑口供不符-男警-我學歷低-口供寫得差/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%AD%E7%94%B7%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6-%E6%88%91%E5%AD%B8%E6%AD%B7%E4%BD%8E-%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E5%AF%AB%E5%BE%97%E5%B7%AE%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=625b952d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%AD%E7%94%B7%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6-%E6%88%91%E5%AD%B8%E6%AD%B7%E4%BD%8E-%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E5%AF%AB%E5%BE%97%E5%B7%AE%2F&h=1b875bdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/聲稱遭男教師拳打-辯方質疑口供不符-男警-我學歷低-口供寫得差/</a><br />\n<br />\n自知之明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ced3fdcf5a681bfb58940d0865ea23a0ce6ab4","tid":2357344,"uid":308567,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:05:49.000Z","msg":"支那人名？ 趙金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f49d0ac18330cb70c93eb4cc99e2de36218312","tid":2357344,"uid":70786,"like":16,"dis